WEBVTT

1
00:01:40.180 --> 00:01:41.810
My!

2
00:01:42.100 --> 00:01:45.150
Look at you putting in 
the effort, Yamada-chan.

3
00:01:45.440 --> 00:01:48.400
I need to follow your example.

4
00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:51.490
You already have 
the perfect smile, Ohno-san.

5
00:01:51.490 --> 00:01:52.990
Do I, now?

6
00:01:52.990 --> 00:01:54.410
Yamada.

7
00:01:54.820 --> 00:01:57.780
Can I ask you for a face shot 
and an interview?

8
00:01:57.780 --> 00:02:01.000
What? Corporate PR stuff again?

9
00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:03.160
At least try to hide 
your displeasure, Yamada.

10
00:02:03.580 --> 00:02:06.420
I mean, I just did one not too long ago.

11
00:02:06.420 --> 00:02:08.290
It is what it is.

12
00:02:08.290 --> 00:02:11.340
You're a nominee for 
the Smile Award again this year.

13
00:02:11.340 --> 00:02:12.670
Wow!

14
00:02:13.130 --> 00:02:14.470
Fine.

15
00:02:14.470 --> 00:02:16.680
Let's get it over and done with!

16
00:02:17.090 --> 00:02:19.350
That's some code-switching skill.

17
00:02:19.350 --> 00:02:22.560
I almost miss the zero-smile Yamada 
from your part-time days.

18
00:09:54.840 --> 00:09:57.850
Okay, that should do it.

19
00:09:57.850 --> 00:09:59.310
Interview done.

20
00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:01.600
You can take your break now.

21
00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:03.270
Hey, boss?

22
00:10:04.520 --> 00:10:06.980
Back when this store had a different name,

23
00:10:06.980 --> 00:10:10.570
there was a guy who snapped at 
a customer who had it out for me.

24
00:10:10.570 --> 00:10:11.690
Remember him?

25
00:10:11.690 --> 00:10:17.200
Huh? Do you have any idea how many 
of those I've seen in all my years here?

26
00:10:17.200 --> 00:10:19.160
Not a chance. 
I don't remember that at all.

27
00:10:20.830 --> 00:10:23.830
Well, even I don't remember his face.

28
00:10:25.250 --> 00:10:29.340
He always smoked by the entrance 
after shopping with us.

29
00:10:30.210 --> 00:10:33.130
He was a man with 
ruffled hair, battered shirts,

30
00:10:33.130 --> 00:10:35.430
and awful bags under his eyes.

31
00:10:40.430 --> 00:10:45.730
He stopped showing up after we 
removed that ashtray due to a complaint.

32
00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:52.110
I wonder if he's still 
smoking somewhere else.
